question: Ellen is required to submit a 250-page dissertation. She already finished writing 1/5 of the dissertation. How many pages does she have left to write?
answer:
Ellen has already written 1/5 of the dissertation which is 250 pages*1/5 = <<250*1/5=50>>50 pages.
So, she still needs to write 250 pages - 50 pages = <<250-50=200>>200 pages.
#### 200
